{"tid":861663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不動嶼山】港人憤怒了！ 萬人遊行反填海","createTime":"2018-10-14T10:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T13:07:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":314,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"ed13c94b2ff238751409b8810cf8ccbcd855bea4","tid":861663,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥在《施政報告》，建議在大嶼山對開填海，面積由今年4月諮詢公眾時的1,000公頃，大幅加碼至1,700公頃。政府消息指，總成本至少4、5千億元，相當於政府近半財政儲備，引起社會嘩然。「守護大嶼聯盟」今日（14日）下午3時在銅鑼灣東角道默站抗議，下午3時半再遊行至政府總部，下午6時半在政總前出席論壇，反對林鄭的「明日大嶼」填海計劃。現場所見，在下午3時已有3,000人於東角道起步，至下午4時半，所有遊行人士才全部離開起步點東角道，記者估計今次遊行有逾萬人參加。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥提出的「明日大嶼」計劃，擬在大嶼山填海1,700公頃，引爆民怨。守護大嶼聯盟今午發起遊行反對填海，在起點銅鑼灣東角道，下午3時有約200名市民集合，高呼「明日香港 我哋話事」口號及高舉「禍留後代」等標語，隨後開始默站。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181014&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58791527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181014%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58791527&d=zoZnPIsdRNAkNaKs3iul9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=17059498\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181014%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58791527&h=b3d9e14d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181014&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58791527</a>"},{"pid":"b78057b398501f92a3baf8bc2d5e81b6bd41d90f","tid":861663,"uid":184679,"like":300,"dislike":2,"score":298,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">身懷六甲媽媽：林鄭逼我大住個肚走出嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n居於西貢的陳小姐現時有六個月身孕，她今午專誠帶同四歲的女兒參加反對「明日大嶼」計劃。陳小姐直言林鄭的人工島計劃荒謬，「完全唔覺得佢有為下一代著想」。她續解釋，一萬億的儲備應投放在教育、醫療範疇上，但林鄭居然以覓地建屋為由，將香港所有儲備用在興建人工島這個嚴重破壞香港的項目上，「你口口聲聲話解決住屋問題，但香港係咪係無地呢？」陳又感觸地表示，當年反國教風波，她同樣挺著大肚子出來參加遊行，從沒想到多年後又要在懷有身孕的情況下為香港下一代未來站出來，「第二次迫到我大住個肚走出嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181014&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58793664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181014%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58793664&d=zoZnPIsdRNAkNaKs3iul9hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=76606405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181014%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58793664&h=45e78be4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181014&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58793664</a>"},{"pid":"6a4f8ea9d94ba4dff517be2e0dc235ddab2edd49","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"574e98557bc7ff09f7b82d6c19b93eda9573c521","tid":861663,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a86ad4c412a159a250cf0dfca1e61773446ef8","tid":861663,"uid":27909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31220ec96e3a5ec909b7e95c99f5c789e9e04c9d","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":213,"dislike":2,"score":211,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"唔好比班勞改五毛誤導以為得3000人，推<br />\n<br />\n屌你班勞毛，等加刑啦！"},{"pid":"e480fa3d22a6e1ff738aa15b9bfb72944772778f","tid":861663,"uid":19278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced445d54b131037ca6c8466bd17cfec2e80741c","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"5b034a4a34ae8fe10461b7be942f08d8dcbebf00","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"126734b97af09c13f7bba11c5a603b00db3cfb3d","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like"