0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bda128c25fc78b3cf20ac5344f5e64003a12bea9","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e994f2dbb8b9f559c0fde3d8911183e84bafe20","tid":861663,"uid":9286,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"香港好快變做集中營城市<br />\n睇下新疆維吾爾族人比中共強姦緊<br />\n下個就到香港 <br />\n<br />\n吸乾庫房<br />\n移民嘅移民<br />\n撤資嘅撤資<br />\n<br />\n好快香港經濟就冧<br />\n變即棄condom<br />\n結局只會同新疆一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港亡 &gt; 家破 &gt; 人亡</span><br />\n<br />\n當全香港人換晒新身份證<br />\n「天網」監控系統就會空降香港<br />\n到時得兩個選擇揀<br />\n做中共走狗 or 自殺<br />\n<br />\n港獨革命迫在眉捷<br />\n再遲就變晒無牙老虎"},{"pid":"1f9b642bf3eb19d5c965d18820708901379778f3","tid":861663,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"黑色五毛警告⚠️現正生效<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/861530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/861530</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"919eb3c1db9c3ef0f76a908a90c834b3236fc604","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b77ac6ae0d1ac2a6d1bacb5db1982ba0ec7f6b53","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb37948d28d6af1a2a02d2ce7d762dc54e24f791","tid":861663,"uid":179908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f46d5cdd226fec42b4d814f16d75f309d087e8","tid":861663,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db498b9418c9d64bb0ebc26f7c8651a0bdc7e65a","tid":861663,"uid":89030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:49:16.000Z"